structure.unit: LICENSING OF MOTOR VEHICLES, OPERATORS, AND TRAILERS

law.history: Repealed 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 139, sec. 33, effective January 1, 1967. -- Amended 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 95, sec. 2. -- Amended 1962 Ky. Acts ch. 62, sec. 5, effective January 1, 1963. -- Amended 1960 Ky. Acts ch. 254, sec. 1. -- Amended 1958 Ky. Acts ch. 70, sec. 25. -- Amended 1956 (2nd Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 5, sec. 2. -- Amended 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 13. -- Amended 1950 Ky. Acts ch. 63, sec. 58, effective June 15, 1950. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 15, sec. 4.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Extra registration fees for trucks having gross weight in excess of 18,000 pounds.
